<p class="eyebrow">Carrier intelligence</p>
<h1>Know where a number routes before you rate, route, or risk-score it.</h1>
<p class="lede">Carrier Lookup returns routing intelligence such as LRN, mobile portability, and carrier-of-record context so telecom teams can make better call-routing, fraud, and cost decisions.</p>
<p class="hero-actions">
	<a class="btn btn-primary" href="/pricing/">See pricing</a>
	<a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/docs/api/">Read API docs</a>
</p>

<section class="section-block">
	<h2>Three workflows, one API</h2>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>For real-time call setup</strong> — LRN lookup at signup time, fraud-check time, or call-setup time. REST and webhook formats.</li>
		<li><strong>For ops teams</strong> — Portal lookup with shareable URLs and exportable history. No API key required for users with portal access.</li>
	</ul>
</section>

